### 1. Create User (ADMIN creates user)
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Leela",
  "email": "leela@gmail.com"
}

### 2. Assign Diet Plan to User (ADMIN action)
POST http://localhost:8080/diet/assign/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "breakfast": "Oats",
  "lunch": "Rice",
  "dinner": "Salad",
  "calories": 1200
}

### 3. Get All Diet Plans
GET http://localhost:8080/diet/all

### 4. Get All Users
GET http://localhost:8080/user/all

### 5. Delete Diet Plan (optional)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/diet/delete/1

### 6. Update Diet Plan (optional)
PUT http://localhost:8080/diet/update/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "breakfast": "Fruits",
  "lunch": "Rice",
  "dinner": "Soup",
  "calories": 1000
}

### Assign Diet Plan with Suggestion
POST http://localhost:8080/diet/assign/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "breakfast": "Oats",
  "lunch": "Rice",
  "dinner": "Salad",
  "calories": 1200,
  "suggestion": "Drink more water and avoid junk food"
}